OL,3,CFormer justice secretary warned Sunak
OL,4,Cof a 'pray date' on prison overcrowding
OL,6,FThe last Conservative justice
OL,7,Fsecretary warned Rishi Sunak that if
OL,8,Fhe failed to introduce an early
OL,9,Fprisoner release scheme (like the one
OL,10,Fthat has been brought in today by
OL,11,FLabour) they might need to "get down
OL,12,Fon their knees and pray" for the
OL,13,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,15,FI can reveal Alex Chalk repeatedly
OL,16,Fspoke to the then prime minister, as
OL,17,Fwell as officials in the Ministry of
OL,18,FJustice (MoJ) and Downing Street,
OL,19,Fabout what he called a "pray-date"
OL,20,Fthat he warned was no later than mid-
OL,21,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
