OL,3,CFormer justice secretary warned Sunak
OL,4,Cof a 'pray date' on prison overcrowding
OL,6,FHe feared that after that point
OL,7,Fovercrowding could get so severe that
OL,8,Fthe police would be forced to
OL,9,Fintroduce Operation Brinker,
OL,10,Feffectively a one-in-one-out system.
OL,12,FOfficials have told me they feared
OL,13,Fthat could result in riots breaking
OL,14,Fout across the country's prison
OL,15,Festates.
