OL,3,CFormer justice secretary warned Sunak
OL,4,Cof a 'pray date' on prison overcrowding
OL,6,FI found out about the conversations
OL,7,Fwhile researching my new book - Taken
OL,8,Fas Red - which comes out later this
OL,9,Fmonth and tracks Keir Starmer's rise
OL,10,Fto power and how the Tories crashed
OL,11,Fout of government.
OL,13,FChalk used the language about a "pray-
OL,14,Fdate" in a meeting with Sunak two days
OL,15,Fbefore the election was announced on
OL,16,FMonday, 20 June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
