OL,3,CFormer justice secretary warned Sunak
OL,4,Cof a 'pray date' on prison overcrowding
OL,6,FSources have suggested that Downing
OL,7,FStreet later indicated to the MoJ that
OL,8,Fthey were willing to go ahead with the
OL,9,Fso-called SDS-40 scheme, in which
OL,10,Fprisoners on particular sentences are
OL,11,Freleased early, 40% of the way through
OL,12,Ftheir sentences rather than 50%.
OL,14,FSo when the election was called on
OL,15,FWednesday, Chalk was said to be
OL,16,Ffurious.
OL,18,FThe conversation came after growing
OL,19,Ftensions between MoJ and Downing
OL,20,FStreet over the question of prison
OL,21,Fovercrowding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
