OL,3,CFormer justice secretary warned Sunak
OL,4,Cof a 'pray date' on prison overcrowding
OL,6,FThe PM described his anger at being
OL,7,Fhanded lists of diminishing prison
OL,8,Fplaces during the riots.
OL,10,FJustice secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,11,Fargued that the government gave
OL,12,Fprobation officers 8 weeks to prepare
OL,13,Fbut many felt that they were not ready.
OL,15,FToday we heard from relatives who
OL,16,Ffeared their loved ones would reoffend
OL,17,Fbecause of a lack of support for
OL,18,Fhousing and benefits.
